docs\TRUTH_TABLE.md:2936:The DINOForge implementation surface — Bridge, ModPlatform, StatModifierSystem (with Reapply), AssetSwap (with name-vs-type fallback), pack hot-reload, HMR signal watcher, MCP tools (21/26 real bridge calls), CLI (17 commands), DumpTools (5), Installer (6), Domain plugins (4/4), schemas (18/20), Registry, NJsonSchema validation, Models (14 classes), pack dependency resolver (Kahn's + cycles), Universe Bible, OverrideApplicator, PackUnitSpawner, WaveInjector, polyglot CI, playCUA binary (built + smoke-tested) — is overwhelmingly REAL.
