.\docs\releases\v0.26.0-pr-body.md:9:DINOForge v0.26.0 is a comprehensive platform maturity release delivering 51 commits across 10 major feature areas with zero breaking changes. The release ships a fully-overhauled F10 mod browser (search, filter, sort, detail panes, conflict resolution), ed25519 pack signing for trusted distribution, in-memory telemetry with a real-time dashboard, full i18n infrastructure (8 locales), and bundled developer tooling (UnityExplorer, AssemblyPublicizer). Six HIGH security findings from the iter-148 code review are patched, and the CI pipeline gains NuGet caching, Windows runners, pack-PR validation, and per-project build gates.
